== Mail lists ==

 * [http://lists.osgeo.org/mailman/listinfo/postgis-users postgis-users] – Discussion of the use and uses of the PostGIS
 * [http://lists.osgeo.org/mailman/listinfo/postgis-devel postgis-devel] – Discussion of ongoing development to the PostGIS; technical issues and debates about changes to the internals of PostGIS belong here
 * [http://lists.osgeo.org/mailman/listinfo/postgis-tickets postgis-tickets] – Automatic notifications from Trac tickets (also called "issues")

== Bug Tracking ==

 * [/newticket Submit a new bug report] (you need to [http://trac.osgeo.org/postgis/login login] with an [http://www.osgeo.org/osgeo_userid OSGeo Userid]). If you need to reset your password use [https://id.osgeo.org/ldap/reset OSGeo profile reset password]
  * Bug reports for the [wiki:WKTRaster PostGIS Raster] extension must have the summary prefixed with '''[raster]''' and the corresponding "raster" component assigned.
    * If possible, provide the output of gdalinfo run upon the source raster.
    * If the bug relates to the raster2pgsql loader, provide the command line parameters you are using.
 * [/report/3 List Open Bugs]
 * [query:status!=closed&type=enhancement&order=id&desc=1,compact List Open Enhancement Requests]

