== PostGIS Extensions ==

List of PostGIS extensions:

=== PostGIS Raster (formerly PostGIS WKT Raster)  ===


 * [http://postgis.net/docs/manual-dev/RT_reference.html Raster functions reference] – This is a list of already implemented functions.  Documentation of functions still in progress.

==== Obsolete
 * [http://trac.osgeo.org/gdal/wiki/frmts_wtkraster.html PostGIS Raster Driver for GDAL] – Information about PostGIS Raster driver for GDAL
 * [wiki:WKTRaster PostGIS Raster] – Integration of a new raster type within PostGIS spec.
 * [wiki:WKTRasterTutorial01 Raster Tutorial] – Demonstrates how to use Raster with vector geometries and install on windows.

